      @Test public void impactTest()
      This method tests for impact method. If the random value generated is less than broken probability of steel brick, the strength of steel brick will become 0 and the steel brick will be broken. if the random value generated is more than broken probability of steel brick, the strength of steel brick will remain as 1 and the steel brick will not break.
